                     <interp inst="t18440916-2336-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp> stealing 1 handkerchief, value 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18440916-name-694" type="victimName">
